<hymn_number>78</hymn_number>
<title>pāo kāi shǔ de de zhuī qiú 迦南78</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 pāo kāi shǔ de de zhuī qiú, qián wǎng líng chéng gāo chù zǒu,
 shì jiè duì wǒ yǐ dàn rán rú shuǐ, shuō shén me fù yǒu xiǎng shòu,
 wǒ de pàn wàng bù shì jīn yǒu, wǒ de shēng mìng yǐ zài zhǔ shǒu.
 nǐ zài shén miàn qián bèi miù ma? bù yào zì zhǎo kǔ tóu,
 róu róu nǐ de yǎn jīng, kàn kàn shì shén me shí hòu, hēi yè yǐ shēn jiāng jìn bái huà,
 bù yào zài tíng liú, bù yào zài tíng liú, zhǔ yǐ zhàn zài mén kǒu.</lyrics>
</song>